## 📋 Hackathon Quick-Start Checklist

Copy this for every hackathon:

```markdown
## [Hackathon Name] — [Date]
### Theme: ___
### Duration: ___ hours
### Team: ___

### Problem Statement Selection
- [ ] Listed 5 candidate problems
- [ ] Scored each with UNIQUE framework
- [ ] Applied 3-Sentence Pitch Test
- [ ] Selected: ___
- [ ] Defined MVP (2-3 features): ___

### Build
- [ ] Project repo created
- [ ] Core feature 1 working
- [ ] Core feature 2 working
- [ ] Deployed to live URL
- [ ] UI polished

### Pitch
- [ ] 5-slide deck ready
- [ ] Demo script rehearsed 3x
- [ ] 5 judge Q&A answers prepared
- [ ] Team roles for pitch assigned

### Post-Hackathon
- [ ] Thank organizers/mentors
- [ ] Publish project on GitHub
- [ ] Write a LinkedIn post about the experience
- [ ] Document learnings for next hackathon
```

